WEBVTT

1
00:05:00.174 --> 00:05:02.510
He's a fucking
Strongsville football player.

2
00:05:04.345 --> 00:05:05.471
He's a running back.

3
00:08:25.713 --> 00:08:28.716
-What a fucking nightmare.
-Go ahead and take a seat.

4
00:08:29.383 --> 00:08:30.676
So. um…

5
00:08:30.760 --> 00:08:33.137
{\an8}-Do you know what time it happened at?
-No. we don't.

6
00:08:33.221 --> 00:08:37.642
{\an8}Right now. it's so early
in the investigation that we don't know.

7
00:08:37.725 --> 00:08:39.727
{\an8}-They fall asleep at the wheel?
-Don't know.

8
00:08:39.810 --> 00:08:43.814
We don't know that.
We don't know that. Um. so--

9
00:08:43.898 --> 00:08:45.316
So two kids are dead.

10
00:08:45.399 --> 00:08:48.361
My son's dead. another kid's dead.
and the girl's in the hospital?

11
00:08:48.444 --> 00:08:50.238
She's in surgery right now.

12
00:08:51.822 --> 00:08:52.990
Fuck.

13
00:08:54.033 --> 00:08:55.701
Oh my gosh.

14
00:09:20.351 --> 00:09:22.937
He texted me at three o'clock
in the morning. "Love you. Dad."

15
00:09:23.020 --> 00:09:25.398
-He texted you at three o'clock?
-2:53.

16
00:09:25.481 --> 00:09:26.732
-2:53.
-Okay.

17
00:44:18.238 --> 00:44:20.991
We've got a few questions for you.

18
00:44:22.201 --> 00:44:25.454
First thing is.
how long have you known Mackenzie?

19
00:44:25.954 --> 00:44:30.125
Probably when I moved to Strongsville.
so ninth grade.

20
00:44:30.209 --> 00:44:33.045
So describe the relationship.

21
00:44:33.545 --> 00:44:34.755
She would be. like…

22
00:44:35.756 --> 00:44:38.050
She was like. "Oh. I love Dom so much."
This and that.

23
00:44:38.133 --> 00:44:40.094
I remember one instance

24
00:44:40.594 --> 00:44:43.764
we were all about to get on the ride.
and Dom was on a phone call.

25
00:44:45.766 --> 00:44:48.310
She was like. "You get on this ride now."

26
00:44:48.394 --> 00:44:50.646
But he said. "I can't right now."

27
00:44:55.067 --> 00:44:58.320
And then we come back.
and she kicked Dom away from us.

28
00:44:58.404 --> 00:45:01.573
And she was just like.
"I'm about to break up with him."

29
00:45:01.657 --> 00:45:03.742
She was just saying stuff like that.

30
00:45:03.826 --> 00:45:06.328
Have you ever heard
Mackenzie threaten Dom?

31
00:45:06.412 --> 00:45:08.664
We were in this candy shop. and. um…

32
00:45:08.747 --> 00:45:11.458
This was after they'd gotten over arguing
and everything.

33
00:45:11.542 --> 00:45:14.294
She was like. "Either buy me something
or shut the fuck up."

34
00:45:14.378 --> 00:45:17.798
She always threatened
and was disrespectful to Dom in my eyes.

35
00:45:17.881 --> 00:45:21.009
Why did Dom put up with this? Do you know?

36
00:45:21.093 --> 00:45:24.430
Um. I've personally been told
that she did voodoo on him.

37
00:45:24.513 --> 00:45:26.098
I mean. I personally don't believe that.

38
00:45:26.181 --> 00:45:29.184
but she has told people
that she's put a spell on him

39
00:45:29.268 --> 00:45:31.603
so that he couldn't break up with her.

40
00:45:34.314 --> 00:45:36.859
Dom had so much going for himself. like…

41
00:45:38.902 --> 00:45:42.364
Why does he stick with Kenzie?
He can do so much better. like.

42
00:45:43.949 --> 00:45:45.075
Okay.

43
00:45:45.159 --> 00:45:48.287
I'm gonna let the prosecutor know
that you came down to talk to us.

44
00:45:48.787 --> 00:45:50.330
Thanks a lot. Appreciate it.

45
00:50:45.751 --> 00:50:49.296
Dom tried to break up with her
multiple times. even in July.

46
00:50:49.379 --> 00:50:52.257
It kept not working out. whatever.
They kept making back up.

47
00:50:55.510 --> 00:50:58.472
Dom would have to call Kenzie's parents.
call her mom and stuff.

48
00:50:58.555 --> 00:51:01.099
and say. "You need to come
get Kenzie outta here."

49
00:51:01.183 --> 00:51:03.685
"She's refusing to leave my house.
She's being crazy."

50
00:51:13.028 --> 00:51:17.574
For me. you know. there's
two types of love that you give somebody.

51
00:51:17.657 --> 00:51:19.826
It's like. "I love that person
unconditionally."

52
00:51:21.995 --> 00:51:25.665
And there's a type of love
that's selfish and restricted

53
00:51:25.749 --> 00:51:27.501
and "I want them all to myself."

54
00:51:27.584 --> 00:51:29.336
And that was Kenzie with Dom.

55
00:51:30.253 --> 00:51:32.672
Kenzie's. like. she's let us know

56
00:51:32.756 --> 00:51:35.801
she will never let go of Dom.

57
00:51:35.884 --> 00:51:39.262
and if she has to let go of Dom.
she will not go on living herself.

58
00:53:01.386 --> 00:53:04.389
-Chris. thanks for coming down.
-Not a problem.

59
00:53:04.472 --> 00:53:07.017
I just wanna ask you
about the incident that happened

60
00:53:07.100 --> 00:53:09.769
<i>before </i>the fatal crash.

61
00:53:10.270 --> 00:53:13.732
Um. Dominic called. and. uh.

62
00:53:14.274 --> 00:53:15.567
he was upset.

63
00:53:15.650 --> 00:53:18.195
and. uh. he was like.
"I'm driving in a car with her.

64
00:53:18.278 --> 00:53:21.323
and I don't wanna be around her anymore.
I'm done."

65
00:53:21.406 --> 00:53:23.158
So I get on the highway.

66
00:53:24.701 --> 00:53:26.828
And I call him. I say. "Where are you at?"

67
00:53:26.912 --> 00:53:30.707
She was like. "I'll crash this car."
I'm like. "Dude. what do you mean?"

68
00:53:31.208 --> 00:53:34.002
Can you clarify again
what you heard her say over the phone?

69
00:53:34.085 --> 00:53:36.630
-She said she'll crash this car.
-You heard her?

70
00:53:36.713 --> 00:53:37.839
-Yes.
-Okay.

71
00:58:23.249 --> 00:58:25.251
Okay. I'm gonna take your handcuffs off.

72
00:58:25.335 --> 00:58:27.795
-I need all the jewelry to come off. okay?
-Okay.

73
00:58:28.296 --> 00:58:29.547
I can't wear any of it?

74
00:58:29.631 --> 00:58:32.425
No. I need you to take it off
while you're in the jail right now.

75
00:58:34.552 --> 00:58:37.055
As soon as we're done.
you'll be able to make a call.

76
00:58:37.138 --> 00:58:39.474
We have to wait
for the detective to come back.

77
00:58:39.557 --> 00:58:41.017
Just have a seat for us.

78
01:11:11.433 --> 01:11:13.602
<i>Dom. open the door.</i>

79
01:11:14.853 --> 01:11:17.314
I can't open the door.
I can't sit here and fight.

80
01:11:17.398 --> 01:11:20.651
We gotta go to dinner
to see my grandparents. I can't…

81
01:11:20.734 --> 01:11:23.237
<i>You're not going to dinner</i>
<i>if you don't open the door.</i>

82
01:11:23.320 --> 01:11:24.738
<i>I'ma let you know that now.</i>

83
01:11:24.822 --> 01:11:26.740
<i>You're gonna come open this door right now</i>

84
01:11:26.824 --> 01:11:29.451
<i>or there's gonna be</i>
<i>a serious fucking problem.</i>

85
01:11:31.161 --> 01:11:35.040
<i>Okay. ready? I'm gonna count to ten.</i>
<i>The door's gonna open. okay?</i>

86
01:11:35.124 --> 01:11:37.501
<i>You're gonna open the door</i>
<i>and stop hiding behind the door</i>

87
01:11:37.584 --> 01:11:39.420
<i>like a little fucking bitch.</i>

88
01:11:39.503 --> 01:11:42.006
Step away from the door.
Maybe I can come outside and talk.

89
01:11:42.089 --> 01:11:43.757
<i>No. we're not fighting outside.</i>

90
01:11:43.841 --> 01:11:46.468
<i>You're gonna open the door right now.</i>

91
01:11:46.552 --> 01:11:48.971
-Why aren't we fighting outside?
-<i>One minute.</i>

92
01:11:49.054 --> 01:11:51.390
Now my mom's trying to call me. I gotta--

93
01:11:51.473 --> 01:11:53.851
<i>No. If you hang up on me.</i>
<i>we're done. I'm leaving.</i>

94
01:11:55.019 --> 01:11:57.938
-Kenzie. there's nothing I can do.
-<i>There is.</i>

95
01:11:58.022 --> 01:11:59.189
<i>Stop being a little bitch.</i>

96
01:11:59.273 --> 01:12:01.108
I can't let you in with how you're acting.

97
01:12:01.191 --> 01:12:02.401
It's as simple as that.

98
01:12:02.484 --> 01:12:04.778
<i>Okay. I'm gonna</i>
<i>break into your house. then.</i>

99
01:12:05.529 --> 01:12:07.948
Dude. what the hell? What the actual fuck?

100
01:12:09.325 --> 01:12:12.911
<i>You don't let me in the house</i>
<i>that I sleep in every night. we are done.</i>

101
01:15:28.857 --> 01:15:30.526
-<i>Mom?</i>
-<i>Hey. hey.</i>

102
01:15:30.609 --> 01:15:32.819
-<i>Oh my goodness.</i>
-<i>I know. Kenzie.</i>

103
01:15:32.903 --> 01:15:35.531
<i>I didn't think</i>
<i>that was gonna happen. She was just like…</i>

104
01:15:35.614 --> 01:15:38.158
<i>She just made it seem</i>
<i>like I was just a murderer.</i>

105
01:15:38.242 --> 01:15:39.826
<i>I know. I know. sweetie.</i>

106
01:16:08.772 --> 01:16:11.358
<i>How much time do you think I'm gonna get?</i>

107
01:16:12.109 --> 01:16:14.027
<i>I'm sure they're gonna go with the max.</i>

108
01:16:14.611 --> 01:16:16.071
-<i>The max?</i>
-<i>Okay?</i>

109
01:22:37.577 --> 01:22:39.871
-Love you. Kenz.
-Love you all.

110
01:22:39.955 --> 01:22:41.122
We know you're innocent.

111
01:25:27.038 --> 01:25:30.125
<i>We're not done yet. okay?</i>
<i>And I can't talk about anything.</i>

112
01:25:31.126 --> 01:25:36.214
<i>So just… have trust in…</i>
<i>have trust in us. please.</i>

113
01:25:36.297 --> 01:25:40.677
<i>Okay? But I'm so sorry. I'm so sorry.</i>

114
01:26:58.796 --> 01:27:00.924
<i>We're gonna fight. fight. fight.</i>

115
01:27:01.424 --> 01:27:03.176
<i>If I have to drive to the White House…</i>

116
01:27:03.676 --> 01:27:06.679
<i>I'll take it all the way</i>
<i>to the Supreme Court if I have to.</i>

